---
description: ExamAITutor UI work must follow the project design system.
globs:
  - "src/**/*.{ts,tsx,css}"
alwaysApply: false
---

Before changing UI, read `design-system/MASTER.md` and, when relevant, `design-system/pages/<page>.md`.

Use shadcn/ui components and semantic Tailwind tokens. Validate mobile at 375px. Keep touch targets at least 44px high, preserve visible focus states, avoid raw hex colors in components, and avoid decorative gradients/orbs.
